<span foreground='Black' weight='bold' size='xx-large'>Deleting a contact</span>

To delete a <b>Contact</b>, first select the <b>Contact</b> in the <b>List</b>. 

Then, mouse down to where you can see the <b>Delete Contact</b> Button,
and delete the <b>Contact</b>.

Additionally, after a <b>Contact</b> is selected on the <b>List</b>, 
you can click on the <b>Edit</b> menu,
and click the <b>Delete Contact</b> Button.
